citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:15-2:00 PM
on 14-Mar-18.
Arrived at the premises and knocked on the door with no answer. Left a voicemail for the registrant and waited 30
minutes prior to leaving.
